data.description:
Welcome to 2314 Hillsdale Ave! This charming home blends modern comfort with a welcoming vibe in a fantastic location. You'll love being close to parks, schools, shops, and dining.

Inside, the smart layout is ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. The updated kitchen is a joy to cook in, and the cozy living area invites relaxation.

The bedrooms offer a cozy retreat, complete with plush carpeting and plenty of storage space. Step outside to your private backyard oasis, perfect for enjoying sunny days and evening gatherings with loved ones.

With a garage and ample driveway space, parking is a breeze. This home has been lovingly maintained inside and out, just waiting for you to make it yours. Don't miss out—schedule a showing today!
